PIQPACC is an acronym, and here's what it
stands for.

Purpose: determine what you want from Gen Al
Information: engage Gen Al to assess the quality of information
Questions: determine how Gen Al can help you empower your questions
Perspectives: have Gen Al help you consider other perspectives
Assumptions: have Gen Al identify, poke, and probe assumptions

Concepts: use Gen Al to make concepts clear
Conclusions: use Gen Al to help distinguish whether conclusions
are opinion-based, truth-based, or fact-based
